{"tid":2374510,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青年藏30煙霧彈押後至2月4日判刑 官關注動機或涉強迫症行為","createTime":"2021-01-21T09:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T11:12:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ccbc99bc3b3de877aa497d2792f17e8a9d1026","tid":2374510,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13117&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=b047728c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13117</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅一庭 <br />\n#祁士偉法官 #判刑<br />\n👤盧(23) #0801天水圍 <br />\n🛑已還押21日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 管有爆炸品<br />\n盧手足被控於2019年8月1日，在天水圍天瑞邨瑞滿樓某單位內明知而管有或控制 #爆炸品，即硝酸鉀、蔗糖、碳酸鎂及碳酸氫鈉的固體混合物。 <br />\n<br />\n(3) #管有物品意圖損壞財產罪<br />\n盧手足被控於在同日同地，管有8支膠管、打火機油、酒精、棉花、玻璃樽和火柴，意圖使用或准許他人用以摧毀或損壞屬於另一人的財產。 <br />\n<br />\n盧手足於2020年12月31日在祁士偉法官席前承認兩項控罪及進行求情，押後至今日判刑，期間需還押索取背景報告，詳情如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12572&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=367d8d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12572</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n辯方大律師以背景報告內容作進一步求情。報告內容指被告對自己的所作所為有濃厚悔意，而犯案動機只是一時衝動魯莽地犯下本案，即使管有但是沒有打算使用涉案物品。<br />\n<br />\n被告意識到行為錯誤亦不合法，承諾不會再犯，明白監禁刑罰無可避免，但希望法庭量刑時可以寬大處理，待被告在服刑完畢，再承擔照顧父母的責任。 <br />\n<br />\n法庭關注被告管有物品的數量、種類不少而且部份是被告自製，難以接納他是因一時衝動而管有涉案物品。祁士偉法官認為有可能顯示被告有強迫症的跡象/先兆，要求先為被告索取心理報告再考慮適當的刑期。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🛑<br />\n押後至2021年2月4日 14:30於區域法院判刑，期間繼續還押。"},{"pid":"19f4dcea94291a2252d80a3833c70daff1ce8915","tid":2374510,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"法官祁士偉對背景報告內容表示關注，指似乎被告有強迫行為，涉及他犯案的動機。辯方強調，被告明白其所為觸犯法律，承諾不會再犯；希望服刑期間好好增值自己，學習一技之長，出獄後承擔起照顧家人的責任。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續指，被告案發時的確沒有想過如何使用涉案物品，可以說是「魯莽」，同意他或需專業協助，法官遂決定替被告索取心理專家報告。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，當日下午近5時，有組織罪案及三合會調查科警員在天水圍巴士站附近截停被告，出示搜查令。被告帶警員回家中搜查，當時母親及姐姐在家。警方找到被告的筆記簿，內有手寫中文化學物質及百分比等的化學方程式；另找到電子磅、篩、飲管等物品，及30個完整和27個未完成的土製裝置，內含爆炸性煙火混合物。<br />\n<br />\n被告的床附近有19支啤酒樽 、10樽火機燃料，5支酒精、綿花、火柴、3包「鎂粉」、3包封口的硝酸鉀以及現金等物品。被告、母親及姐姐三人被捕，被告承認在廚房搜到物料屬他所有，筆記簿上的字迹亦屬他，而現金則是屬於母親。爆炸品處理科人員化驗5個涉案物質樣本，均驗出硝酸鉀及蔗糖等物質，其餘物質以安全理由銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/HWYQSNFP2RAYXMV2MHJIQFE2CE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FHWYQSNFP2RAYXMV2MHJIQFE2CE%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=7e56dd4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FHWYQSNFP2RAYXMV2MHJIQFE2CE%2F&h=83d42b62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/HWYQSNFP2RAYXMV2MHJIQFE2CE/</a>"},{"pid":"2a3c26d1f0a8069aae5a4433f44a026765980143","tid":2374510,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdd739c5f2050c57021d4e234cdbf0d945bac9b","tid":2374510,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e6ad6a02c509fc6b2beeea9517d8eb68a04977","tid":2374510,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baba032255cd5ba553138f98561cc4b27bbdaa8","tid":2374510,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebad6ee33350bbd8043e102c8b1950bd29c4546","tid":2374510,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9818717b3f0b58c1226a8958e7c7167b0e07a90c","tid":2374510,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"原還押至今日判刑，惟法官今指考慮涉案煙霧彈數量頗多，及閱讀被告背景報告內容後，關注被告或涉強迫行為等問題，決定為被告索取一份心理報告，將判刑押後至下月4日，期間被告續被還押。<br />\n<br />\n被告與在場的母親及姊姊一同被捕，罪名為「管有炸藥」。被告警誡下承認涉案物品屬於他。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/23-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F-30-%E6%9E%9A%E8%97%8F%E7%85%99%E9%9C%A7%E5%BD%88-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E5%BC%B7%E8%BF%AB%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E7%B4%A2%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F23-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F-30-%25E6%259E%259A%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%2585%2599%25E9%259C%25A7%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=66d87604\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F23-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F-30-%25E6%259E%259A%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%2585%2599%25E9%259C%25A7%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=f625f581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/23-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F-30-%E6%9E%9A%E8%97%8F%E7%85%99%E9%9C%A7%E5%BD%88-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E5%BC%B7%E8%BF%AB%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E7%B4%A2%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/</a>"},{"pid":"90c0d8aaffc0074b2d1c4abfaf4c3743d736f079","tid":2374510,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e9c97ea7eef826e276f029cb30c0d6e1be39b5","tid":2374510,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"自己屋企實驗唔得？"},{"pid":"a9ac6204009fb63f70ecfb4a8fc9a4e774fde1c4","tid":2374510,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}